{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Buy Old City Transport Station!</strong></h2>Streets are getting congested with traffic and you can become the solution. Rebuild and run the old city depot. Experience a realistic simulator game of being a public transport manager.<br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1927420/extras/03_renovate.gif?t=1725028862\" /><br>Get rid of debris and junk so that you can start working. Clean the station and repair the vehicles. Buy what cannot be repaired. Get your equipment to working condition and start you service so you can earn more money for further improvements.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1927420/extras/02_customize.gif?t=1725028862\" /><br>Give the city depot your personal touch. The game offers a wide array of options to customize. Every part of a bus or a tram can be changed. Remember, it's not only about making your depot look nice. The better your depot looks, the more money you will make.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1927420/extras/04_hire.gif?t=1725028862\" /><br>Running a city is not a one person job. You can hire drivers and other employees to help you with various tasks. Pay attention during the interview as every candidate has different traits.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1927420/extras/01_drive.gif?t=1725028862\" /><br>Take a break and try your skills as a driver. Choose one of your vehicles and go to town!","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1927420/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1725028862","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1927420/page.bg.jpg?t=1725028862","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1927420/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1725028862","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1927420/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1725028862","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Buy Old City Transport Station!</strong></h2>Streets are getting congested with traffic and you can become the solution. Rebuild and run the old city depot. Experience a realistic simulator game of being a public transport manager.<br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1927420/extras/03_renovate.gif?t=1725028862\" /><br>Get rid of debris and junk so that you can start working. Clean the station and repair the vehicles. Buy what cannot be repaired. Get your equipment to working condition and start you service so you can earn more money for further improvements.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1927420/extras/02_customize.gif?t=1725028862\" /><br>Give the city depot your personal touch. The game offers a wide array of options to customize. Every part of a bus or a tram can be changed. Remember, it's not only about making your depot look nice. The better your depot looks, the more money you will make.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1927420/extras/04_hire.gif?t=1725028862\" /><br>Running a city is not a one person job. You can hire drivers and other employees to help you with various tasks. Pay attention during the interview as every candidate has different traits.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1927420/extras/01_drive.gif?t=1725028862\" /><br>Take a break and try your skills as a driver. Choose one of your vehicles and go to town!","developers":["Creativity AR","Mobilway